-- France Warned by European Commission on Energy, Power Grid, Les Echos Says
-- Tara Patel
-- 2010-06-28T06:19:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/france-warned-by-european-commission-on-energy-power-grid-les-echos-says.html

          
          
             The European Commission has warned
France that Electricite de France SA’s wholly owned power grid
Reseau de Transport de l’Electricite doesn’t publish enough
information about power capacity,  Les Echos  reported, citing
information from the commission.  
 France was also warned about flows through its gas network
don’t meet Europe’s energy market rules, according to the
newspaper report, which said the country was one of 20 found not
to abide by the second energy package of regulations.  
